description:
Men do not ask women out enough. They are terrified that they will get rejected. Well, you might get rejected but you'll survive if that happens and you'll find someone else to ask out. Emily's cohost Menace demonstrates how to ask someone out by calling up a woman he's interested in and asking her out. You're never going to get out of the friend zone if you don't ask them out! Menace also shares he's secrets for lasting longer in bed. Please support our sponsors: Max4Men, Masque, and Good Vibrations. Use coupon code Emily25 at checkout for 25% off your purchase at Max4Men. Use coupon code GVEmily20 at checkout for 20% off purchases of $100 or more at Good Vibrations.
